Hey there moparscapians! :P
Base: Devolution 7.0 [center]Credits[/center]
[ul][li]Ar-temi-s[/li] [li]Bakatool[/li] [li]winten[/li][/ul]
I've been working on my Source for the past few days o.O And i must say, it's looking pretty good =p
This is going to be a classic 317. :) What does that mean?
Class 317 - There will only be old Runescape Items, meaning no god swords, no dragon boots, no 3rd age, no 'dfs'!
Item's Included
[ul][li]Defenders[/li] [li]Fighter Torso[/li] [li]Skill Capes[/li][/ul]
[center]Features[/center]
[ul][li]Members World[/li] [li]Free World[/li] [li]Modern Magic[/li] [li]Ancient Magic[/li] [li]All Specials Working[/li] [li]Character File Saving saves on Both Sources.[/li] [li]Character File Loading loads from Both Sources.[/li] [li]'Member's Object' On Free World Client/Source.[/li] [li]Good Eating Handler.[/li] [li]Good Weapon Switching Timer.[/li] [li]100% Prayers[/li][/ul]
